Text: Enjoy this rare PBS gem about sperm whales feeding off Alaska, Mexico, and Hawaii!
Oops, they are humpback whales, not sperm whales. This video of the humpback whales with their babies, of them feeding, and breaching, and singing is truly amazing.

OK people, I have seeded this thoroughly, but more people need to join in the seeding effort. 

This video is a spectacular account of humpback whale life!
